id: pm-tcw1
title: "preflightExtension(blueprint, options) — pure unified author-time analyzer (compose.ts)"
description: "Add the pure synchronous capstone to src/sdk/compose.ts. Given a blueprint and { identity?, target?, declaredCapabilities? }, runs lintExtensionBlueprint, optionally synthesizes the manifest (when identity given), optionally runs checkExtensionManifestCompatibility against the synthesized/blueprint bounds (when target given), and returns ExtensionPreflightReport { ok, capabilities, blueprint, manifest, compatibility, findings } where findings are tagged by source (blueprint|compatibility). Reuses blueprintResult.used to avoid a second deriveExtensionCapabilities call."
