resolution: "Added pure synchronous preflightExtension(blueprint, options) returning ExtensionPreflightReport { ok, capabilities, blueprint, manifest, compatibility, findings }. Runs lintExtensionBlueprint always; synthesizes manifest when identity given; runs checkExtensionManifestCompatibility against synthesized/blueprint bounds when target given. Findings are flattened + source-tagged (blueprint|compatibility); the now-moot manifest_capabilities_absent advisory is curated out of the consolidated view once a manifest is synthesized (raw lint kept on report.blueprint). Reuses blueprintResult.used (no second derive)."
expected_result: One-call author-time analyzer unifying the three separate checks.
actual_result: Delivered; 100% covered; barrel re-export via export * from compose.js.
